metadata.title: RadioShack 9-Inch Y-Adapter Audio Cable
features: Copper center conductor for superior signal transfer keeps out annoying electrical interference
Accepts 2 phono (RCA) plugs; fits 1 mono 1/4" stereo phone plug
description: Maximize your A/V signal transfer for optimum sound with this premium cable's high-quality connectors, which substantially reduce signal loss. RadioShack Gold Series connectors are designed to enhance the performance of your audio and video components by reducing signal loss and interference. Low-capacitance connectors deliver the most dynamic, distortion-free signals your system can provide. Use this premium model to combine or split audio signals between components.
